title: S3 EP2: Mailbox Money feat. Allison Zamora
itunes:title: Mailbox Money feat. Allison Zamora
description: Today we talk about fashion licensing. Allison Zamora is a licensing executive who started her career at Calvin Klein and later went to LVMH. She walks us through the mechanism of licensing and how it's changed over the years.
